Package: tradeio
Title: Data Acquisition and Normalization for TradingVerse
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("TradingVerse", "Core Team", , "tradingverse@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides unified interface for fetching financial market data from 
    multiple sources including Yahoo Finance, Alpha Vantage, FRED, and local files.
    Automatically normalizes data into the TradingVerse market_tbl format with proper
    timezone handling, missing data treatment, and corporate actions adjustments.
